      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "1.     Implement behavior change communication activities supported for increasing awareness and adoption of maternal, newborn, child health and nutrition practices especially of socially excluded, and marginalized groups in DACAW districts.\r\n2.     Mobilize youth as community advocates for maternal, newborn and child health and nutrition related care and practices.\r\n3.     Health and nutrition related activities promoted through child clubs, mothers groups and WATCH groups in DACAW districts. \r\n4.   Develop National hand washing with soap and water Strategy & Action plan and its operationalisation in cooperation with government, NGOs and Private sector"
